check the webserver on loaclhost:8080 or directly from Docker Desktop browse which is displaying the Home Page as desired and accessed from local system browser
Push this Image to Docker Hub as V2.

PS C:\Users\DELL> docker tag webserver1:latest omeshwar/omjyokan:webserver-v2
PS C:\Users\DELL> docker push omeshwar/omjyokan:webserver-v2
